%%{init: {"sequence": {"mirrorActors": false}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    actor Manager
    participant UI as Bottleneck View
    participant API as Backend API
    participant ML as Python ML Server
    participant DB as Database
    participant Notify as Alerts

    Manager->>UI: Open Workflow Analytics
    UI->>API: GET /api/analytics/bottlenecks

    API->>DB: Fetch all active tasks
    DB-->>API: Task List

    loop For each task
        API->>ML: POST /analyze_task
        ML-->>API: { urgency_score, urgency_label }
    end

    API->>API: Group by Column/Status
    API->>API: Calculate Average Urgency per Column
    
    alt Avg Urgency > Threshold
        API->>API: Flag Column Bottleneck
    end
    
    API->>API: Group by Assignee
    API->>API: Count "Critical" urgency tasks per person
    
    alt Critical Count > 3
        API->>API: Flag Person Bottleneck (Overloaded)
    end

    API-->>UI: Bottleneck Data (aggregated)

    UI->>UI: Render Heatmaps & Alerts
    UI-->>Manager: Display Bottleneck Dashboard

    alt Critical Overload Detected
        UI->>UI: Show Red Alert
        API->>Notify: Send System Alert
    end

    Manager->>UI: Click "High Urgency" Column
    UI->>API: GET /api/tasks?min_urgency=80
    API-->>UI: List of burning tasks

